Titolo: Mach Rider

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Mach Rider is a futuristic vehicular combat video game created by Nintendo. It was first released in Japan in 1985 for the Nintendo Family Computer, and then in North America a year later for the Nintendo Entertainment System, and in 1987 for the PAL region. Later it was released on the Virtual Console for the Wii (2007), Nintendo 3DS (2013) and Wii U (2014).The Japanese Famicom release can use the Famicom Data Recorder to save custom tracks. This feature was missing from the American and European releases, but was retained in all versions of the Virtual Console release except for the 3DS version.